Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.76,0:00:17.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, don't you think it's weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.93,0:00:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, Saya?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.89,0:00:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is Fuyumi in the middle?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.23,0:00:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.89,0:00:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You all know who should take the number one spot to attract more attention, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.23,0:00:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.24,0:00:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.86,0:00:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.66,0:00:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's not that...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.32,0:00:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me who has to stay in the middle!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.74,0:00:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-E!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.95,0:00:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's not me, it's absurd.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.00,0:00:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is...?
