Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.01,0:02:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right! Left! Right! Left!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.18,0:02:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.31,0:02:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomo-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.31,0:02:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.65,0:02:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We stop here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.69,0:02:35.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Train so that you six synchronize better.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.98,0:02:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.40,0:02:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's all try our best.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.24,0:02:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Team work!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.07,0:02:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.24,0:02:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miki-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.70,0:02:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's the radio interview after this...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.67,0:02:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She has other appointments now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.29,0:02:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.38,0:02:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"PIN" work?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.96,0:02:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... I don't know what's it about...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.55,0:03:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's so funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.05,0:03:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Less rivals, better, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.89,0:03:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rivals?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.94,0:03:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And today's guests are the new members of Lemon Angel!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.73,0:03:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goo-...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.40,0:03:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good Afternoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.69,0:03:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Looks like the members were decided through a test...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.53,0:03:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Yes... and like I imagined, many viewrs went and I got nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.91,0:03:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Heh... and the other members, how was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.51,0:03:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}This girl didn't speak at all in the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.33,0:03:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Eh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.54,0:03:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.34,0:03:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I got nervous with the mistake I made!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.17,0:03:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You chose a piece from the ones Yui selected during debuts.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.14,0:03:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Yes, exactly. As her older sister I thought "What will become of her"!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.14,0:03:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.35,0:03:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And... what shall we do with the main singer?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.98,0:03:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}So now, let me ask about your dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.48,0:03:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For now, I think only Minaguchi Tomo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.77,0:04:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Well... In my dream there was a big cage, but when I woke up, it disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.28,0:04:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Hey, not THAT dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.95,0:04:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}And your dream, Fuyumi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.03,0:04:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I want to be any kind of artist.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.66,0:04:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're newbies, but don't they hold their upper lip stiff?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.91,0:04:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}To be... But aren't you already a Lemon Angel?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.50,0:04:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Ah, something different from Lemon Angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.75,0:04:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.50,0:04:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Ah, no! Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.00,0:04:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}What do you mean by different? You're thinking of abandoning Lemon Angel in the middle?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.63,0:04:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Yumi? Is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.46,0:04:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}That's a shock!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.67,0:04:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}No, it's not that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.84,0:04:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I guess she's apt...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.84,0:04:25.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagisa Miru.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.76,0:04:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.64,0:04:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you analyze the capacity to sing, only she is appropriate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.63,0:04:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miru?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.22,0:04:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}So, and your dream Miru-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.81,0:04:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.77,0:04:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I want to be Ann.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.61,0:04:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Ann as in Ann the first Angel, I want to be the main singer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.28,0:04:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Miru-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.45,0:04:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like that's what she wants...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.28,0:04:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.07,0:04:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An audition!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.08,0:04:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.08,0:04:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minaguchi or Nagisa, we'll decide who is going to be the main singer through a test.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.42,0:04:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.96,0:04:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}These were the new Lemon Angel members!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.04,0:05:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.63,0:05:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you all decided on your signatures for the autographs this afternoon?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.35,0:05:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,AH!? The signature? What do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.52,0:05:14.64,Default Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, it's easy... Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.74,0:05:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Látod!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.19,0:05:18.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow... incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.86,0:05:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.44,0:05:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.11,0:05:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow... cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.49,0:05:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And yours Yumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.45,0:05:28.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahm... I thought about it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.82,0:05:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.08,0:05:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think it's cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.58,0:05:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's cute, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.08,0:05:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't really call that a signature...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.87,0:05:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry... I was having fun while I was writing, and so...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.21,0:05:41.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And yours, Miru-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.05,0:05:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beautiful handwriting, but isn't that Shuuji?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.09,0:05:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And yours, Tomo?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.22,0:05:49.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, please write!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.68,0:05:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.85,0:05:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's... writing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.23,0:05:58.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Japanese worm!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.85,0:06:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, isn't that a bit cruel?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.44,0:06:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not so bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.90,0:06:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.32,0:06:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You all got together to make fun of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.15,0:06:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kogure-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.82,0:06:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.24,0:06:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kogure-san is choosing the song for your debut.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.33,0:06:17.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.33,0:06:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Debut song...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.37,0:06:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But is it alright to let him choose such an important piece?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.17,0:06:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't look too dependable...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.97,0:06:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday there was a time when Nani-sensei was very mad with him.  
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.35,0:06:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it true?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.56,0:06:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Gure is working hard in his own way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.23,0:06:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gure?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.73,0:06:42.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I decided that his nickname will be Gure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.31,0:06:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.86,0:06:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Poor fellow, you shouldn't nickname him without him being here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.20,0:06:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's to nickname someone, nickname someone who is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.70,0:06:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rabbit!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.45,0:06:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rabbit? Now that i think of it, Gure's better!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.62,0:06:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's decided!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.50,0:07:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.46,0:07:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be a cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.80,0:07:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Himuro and Kudou?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.30,0:07:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And also Kazanaho.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.03,0:07:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miki? Weren't you supposed to be in the interview?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.11,0:07:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not my work.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.62,0:07:38.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But when you, the leader, aren't there, the group discipline will...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.08,0:07:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway,go to where everyone is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.71,0:07:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're late!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.38,0:07:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we really do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.05,0:07:57.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it came as a confirmation from her. There's no mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.43,0:07:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it a trap?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.27,0:08:01.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your job to examine, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.89,0:08:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it... Let me work steadily.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.44,0:08:08.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's late.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.03,0:08:12.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Normally you're all getting along fine, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.86,0:08:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, because we all respect each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.03,0:08:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Saya, you always say that i'm a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.91,0:08:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't say unnecessary things!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.67,0:08:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too... Saya-san always gets mad at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.34,0:08:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, it's all a joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.84,0:08:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a joke... Saya's eyes are always serious when she speaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.26,0:08:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahhh... Leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.76,0:08:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No need to stay so thoughtful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.60,0:08:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.02,0:08:47.15,Default Ext,,0000,0000,0000,,What were those three doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.23,0:08:51.48,Default Ext,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be... again...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.74,0:08:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An internal audition?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.07,0:08:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.95,0:09:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoever wins this internal audition will be the new main vocal of Lemon Angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.50,0:09:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ones who will participate in this audition will be Miru and Tomo, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.54,0:09:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.30,0:09:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a minute...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.88,0:09:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't agree with that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.01,0:09:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.63,0:09:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why only these two?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.84,0:09:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's because--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.60,0:09:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Normally, the best one is chosen to be the lead, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.02,0:09:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.81,0:09:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's like that, I'm the main one!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.27,0:09:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you start with that opinion...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.78,0:09:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say it, Gure!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.69,0:09:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? "Gure"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.57,0:09:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! I invented it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.53,0:09:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fits nicely.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.66,0:09:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, without my permission!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.03,0:09:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gure, I'll also participate in this audition.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.33,0:09:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.00,0:09:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to face the producer?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.67,0:09:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gure, stay quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.63,0:09:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Erika and Fuyumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.00,0:09:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.59,0:09:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave this to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.67,0:09:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, it will be the three of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.93,0:09:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't expecting this...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.93,0:10:00.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miru and Tomo, you'll participate?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.60,0:10:02.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.47,0:10:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be Ann.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.48,0:10:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If there's no other way than to do it, I'll become the new Ann.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.28,0:10:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miru-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.24,0:10:27.87,Default Alt Ext,,0000,0000,0000,,So, this Saturday, at 1700 hours, the internal audition will be held.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.42,0:10:31.38,Default Alt Ext,,0000,0000,0000,,The participants will be Saya and Miru, and also Tomo, These three.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.75,0:10:32.33,Default Alt Ext,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this Ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.54,0:10:33.21,Default Alt Ext,,0000,0000,0000,,It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.67,0:10:37.97,Default Ext,,0000,0000,0000,,This Saturday. 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.59,0:10:42.47,Default Alt Ext,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Next Saturday?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.10,0:10:47.43,Default Alt Ext,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see... actually Himuro asked you to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.81,0:10:53.69,Default Ext,,0000,0000,0000,,Yui-senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.09,0:10:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.65,0:11:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll really be back by the afternoon, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.65,0:11:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.53,0:11:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't take much time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.65,0:11:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, got it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.11,0:11:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the afternoon--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.11,0:11:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only... if you yourself choose to go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.74,0:11:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you'll choose otherwise.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.46,0:11:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Himuro Shinya's studio.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.97,0:12:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.95,0:12:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Drums,I don't need you anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.37,0:12:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not following my instructions...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.87,0:12:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're instructions?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.04,0:12:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. I'm not your robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.42,0:12:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can improvise a bit, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.88,0:12:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No need to improvise beyond the arrangement which I've done.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.59,0:12:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.55,0:12:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that music?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.13,0:12:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.51,0:12:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is your "live music"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.30,0:12:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.85,0:12:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.68,0:12:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.43,0:12:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Himuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.73,0:12:59.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.36,0:13:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.46,0:13:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Working together with Himuro Shinya was Kohno Yui's dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.88,0:13:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.63,0:13:29.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lemon Angel was born with a Kohno Yui and Himuro Shinya collaboration.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.43,0:13:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.51,0:13:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And why's it necessary to continue without him now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.60,0:13:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.81,0:13:41.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lemon Angel, without Himuro, will not make the expected success.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.82,0:13:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suwa Miki and Kogure only want to use the Lemon Angel's name to win money.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.20,0:13:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's wrong, the two aren't...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.41,0:13:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So why not make exactly like the original?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.95,0:13:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because Himuro transmits the Kohno Yui's spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.78,0:14:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.86,0:14:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have anymore time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.61,0:14:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave her be.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.49,0:14:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't choose as the main singer a person who is late to an important test.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.92,0:14:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miki-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.43,0:14:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't today the test for the main vocal?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.72,0:14:53.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because, senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.14,0:15:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, until a while ago, I was at Himuro's studio...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.06,0:15:03.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Himuro?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.07,0:15:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind if you want to quit being a Lemon Angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.99,0:15:21.00,Betétdal Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Sakura no hanabira hirahira maifurite ikuyouni
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.99,0:15:21.00,Betétdal_HUN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Cherry petals fall like snow
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.79,0:15:22.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to the truth about Yui's death and then decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.00,0:15:23.75,Betétdal Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Odayakana
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.00,0:15:23.75,Betétdal_HUN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Calmly
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.88,0:15:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.50,0:15:32.59,Betétdal Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kokoro hitoride mitsumeteta
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.50,0:15:32.59,Betétdal_HUN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Looking for only a unique soul
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.97,0:15:39.64,Betétdal Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kanashiniha ataerareta wakega aru
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.97,0:15:39.64,Betétdal_HUN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Has a reason to offer
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.19,0:15:42.60,Betétdal Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Dareni demo
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.19,0:15:42.60,Betétdal_HUN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}To anyone
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.06,0:15:53.29,Betétdal Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Yasashisano tane naraba kichinto sodate ikou
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.06,0:15:53.29,Betétdal_HUN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Treat well the goodness' seeds.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.24,0:15:44.73,Default Ext,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe... I could be like Ann.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.70,0:15:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miru's song is really very nice.  
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.34,0:15:58.29,Betétdal Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I promise you kitto
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.34,0:15:58.29,Betétdal_HUN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I surely promise you
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.57,0:15:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, and mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.16,0:15:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course Saya's song was also good!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.23,0:15:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You make it sound like mine was worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.95,0:16:04.50,Betétdal Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Don't look back kitto
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.95,0:16:04.50,Betétdal_HUN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Don't look back, surely
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.54,0:16:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.63,0:16:09.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.13,0:16:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to Tomo?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.93,0:16:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it continues like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.26,0:16:17.85,Default Ext,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.68,0:16:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for being late!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.77,0:16:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.77,0:16:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're late!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.94,0:16:27.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.02,0:16:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomo, you can sing, can't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.03,0:16:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.29,0:16:46.25,Default Ext,,0000,0000,0000,,Yui-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.50,0:16:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Almost a year and a half ago, Yui and I built an artificial intelligence named Lemon Angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.47,0:16:59.81,Betétdal Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Nagai kaidan nobori tsuzukete
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.47,0:16:59.81,Betétdal_HUN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Climbing the long stairs
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.64,0:17:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Through Nouvelle, Angel was exposed to the public and attracted a lot of attention. 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.91,0:17:06.74,Betétdal Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Tadoritsuita doa nokku shita no
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.91,0:17:06.74,Betétdal_HUN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}When I arrived, I knocked at the door
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.14,0:17:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Nouvelle, thinking that this project would be good business...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.84,0:17:12.19,Betétdal Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Omoi tobiraga hiraite soshite
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.84,0:17:12.19,Betétdal_HUN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Opening the heavy door
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.27,0:17:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...hired a producer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.36,0:17:20.66,Betétdal Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Deaeru hazu, datta... Minna no egao ni
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.36,0:17:20.66,Betétdal_HUN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I surely would find ... Everyone with happy faces
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.74,0:17:14.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That producer was Himuro Shinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.63,0:17:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the Angels were changing like that man directed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.62,0:17:28.88,Betétdal Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Doushite? Maru de shiranai hito mitai
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.62,0:17:28.88,Betétdal_HUN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Why? They look like unknown people
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.54,0:17:38.89,Betétdal Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Doushite? Tsumetai kotoba kizutsukeru
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.54,0:17:38.89,Betétdal_HUN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Why? The cold words hurt
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.84,0:17:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like that, they were nothing but marionettes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.51,0:17:34.97,Default Alt Ext,,0000,0000,0000,,This sort of music isn't yours, Yui!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.13,0:17:38.39,Default Alt Ext,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't the Lemon Angels you wanted to build.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.13,0:17:42.06,Default Alt Ext,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that, but it's no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.14,0:17:41.13,Betétdal Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Searching for myself
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.14,0:17:41.13,Betétdal_HUN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Searching for myself
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.43,0:17:52.91,Betétdal Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Hajimete no kanjou hitomi kumorasete
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.43,0:17:52.91,Betétdal_HUN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}The iris, the first feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.06,0:17:42.64,Default Alt Ext,,0000,0000,0000,,Why!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.64,0:17:46.31,Default Alt Ext,,0000,0000,0000,,Taking that man off the project is easy, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.06,0:17:47.98,Default Alt Ext,,0000,0000,0000,,If it continues like this, that man...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.98,0:17:48.60,Default Alt Ext,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.61,0:17:52.40,Default Alt Ext,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop speaking bad about him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.08,0:17:54.78,Betétdal Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Searching for myself
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.08,0:17:54.78,Betétdal_HUN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Searching for myself
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.09,0:18:00.73,Betétdal Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Utagau koto shika dekinaku narisou
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.09,0:18:00.73,Betétdal_HUN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Maybe I could only reach
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.20,0:18:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yui, trapped between her feelings for Lemon Angels and her love for Himuro,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.86,0:18:12.71,Betétdal Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kono mamaja iya hayaku ~Watashi wo Sagashite~
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.86,0:18:12.71,Betétdal_HUN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Don't want to be like this fast ~Find me~
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.41,0:18:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,thought about a solution.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.20,0:18:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was to hack the Lemon Angels and destroy that archive.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.71,0:18:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Posing as a hacker named Arukan whom she invented, she destroyed the Artificial Intelligence that she built herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.72,0:18:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With that, she thought she was finally free.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.39,0:18:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then she told him about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.73,0:18:31.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that man told Yui to rebuild those archives.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.19,0:18:35.57,Betétdal Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Nagai yume kara mezameteshimau
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.19,0:18:35.57,Betétdal_HUN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I just woke up from a long dream
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.19,0:18:32.65,Default Alt Ext,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.57,0:18:34.44,Default Alt Ext,,0000,0000,0000,,So what was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.24,0:18:36.65,Default Alt Ext,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by "What was that?"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.88,0:18:42.49,Betétdal Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Mabushi suguiru sora zutto miteru
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.88,0:18:42.49,Betétdal_HUN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I look toward a very bright sky
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.25,0:18:38.49,Default Alt Ext,,0000,0000,0000,,Me... you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.49,0:18:41.32,Default Alt Ext,,0000,0000,0000,,Yui, you're a very talented person.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.29,0:18:44.66,Default Alt Ext,,0000,0000,0000,,But looks like your mistaking things.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.49,0:18:48.09,Betétdal Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kagami no naka no kokoro ha kitto
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.49,0:18:48.09,Betétdal_HUN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Surely, the soul inside the mirror
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.33,0:18:49.79,Default Alt Ext,,0000,0000,0000,,I have absolutely no interest in you, unless it's for the programs that you make.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.21,0:18:57.21,Betétdal Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Naiteru hazu, nanoni ... kinou to onnaji ne
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.21,0:18:57.21,Betétdal_HUN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Surely, it's crying ... like yesterday
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.55,0:18:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For him, flirting with Yui was nothing important. 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.47,0:19:04.85,Betétdal Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Doushite? Nanimo nakatta koto ni shite
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.47,0:19:04.85,Betétdal_HUN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Why pretend that nothing happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.55,0:19:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He only wanted a program that could give economic power to his own music.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.07,0:19:14.98,Betétdal Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Doushite? Onnaji uta wo utaeru no?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.07,0:19:14.98,Betétdal_HUN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Why can't I sing the same music?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.27,0:19:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And when after that illusion-shattering conversation, Yui left Nouvelle... 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.08,0:19:17.15,Betétdal Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Searching for myself
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.08,0:19:17.15,Betétdal_HUN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Searching for myself
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.44,0:19:28.96,Betétdal Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Hajimete no henka wo chanto uketomeyou
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.44,0:19:28.96,Betétdal_HUN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Accept perfectly the first transformation
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.46,0:19:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.57,0:19:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-So Yui-senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.74,0:19:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What you'll do, is left for you to decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.06,0:19:30.91,Betétdal Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Searching for myself
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.06,0:19:30.91,Betétdal_HUN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Searching for myself
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.07,0:19:36.05,Betétdal Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Inouru you ni tada mamoru to shiteru
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.07,0:19:36.05,Betétdal_HUN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Trying to protect me through prayers
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.71,0:19:48.88,Betétdal Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Tsuyokunaritai no dakara ~Watashi wo Sagashite~
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.71,0:19:48.88,Betétdal_HUN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I want to be strong so ~Find me~
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.38,0:19:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ohh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.80,0:19:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomo song... sure has changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.60,0:19:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it now touches the soul deeper.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.39,0:20:02.65,Betétdal Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Hoshi mo mienai to iu kono machi no yoru demo
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.39,0:20:02.65,Betétdal_HUN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Even in this town that you don't see stars at night
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.81,0:19:53.35,Default Ext,,0000,0000,0000,,That is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.07,0:19:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.66,0:20:03.05,Default Ext,,0000,0000,0000,,...Ann.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.20,0:20:12.75,Betétdal Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Chiisa na hikari sagasu youni...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.20,0:20:12.75,Betétdal_HUN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Like searching for a little light...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.84,0:20:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomo is really good!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.67,0:20:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got all emotional!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.38,0:20:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In addition to coming late, you made us listen to a song like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.10,0:20:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't help it, I acknowledge you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.22,0:20:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saya!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.68,0:20:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make Tomo the main singer!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.06,0:20:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.23,0:20:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It has to be her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.03,0:20:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's ok, Tomo?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.28,0:20:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's decided. Well, it means she's not so useless after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.51,0:21:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yui.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.52,0:21:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I could have been Ann, but you can surpass her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.28,0:21:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Miru-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.83,0:21:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.29,0:21:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, it's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.87,0:21:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll build the real Lemon Angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.59,0:21:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ok, with Himuro?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.30,0:21:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.92,0:21:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.30,0:21:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to sing Yui-senpai's music with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.72,0:21:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll regret it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.89,0:21:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I regret it...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.12,0:22:07.80,Ed Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}hajimete negatta hi kara
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.12,0:22:07.80,ED Hun,,0000,0000,0000,,Since the first day i laid eyes on you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.15,0:22:16.14,Ed Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}nazeka kokoro ga nemuren nakunatte
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.15,0:22:16.14,ED Hun,,0000,0000,0000,,For some reason my heart can't seem to rest
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.44,0:22:24.90,Ed Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}denwa wa suru yuuki mo nai kawari
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.44,0:22:24.90,ED Hun,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have the courage to pick up the phone and call.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.07,0:22:34.79,Ed Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}toomawari guuzen wo kiri
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.07,0:22:34.79,ED Hun,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, if for only a chance
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.21,0:22:39.71,Ed Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}onna no ko tachi wa
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.21,0:22:39.71,ED Hun,,0000,0000,0000,,When girls
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.86,0:22:43.50,Ed Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}koi wo suru ta bi ni
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.86,0:22:43.50,ED Hun,,0000,0000,0000,,are in love...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.72,0:22:49.66,Ed Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}sabishigari ni naru
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.72,0:22:49.66,ED Hun,,0000,0000,0000,,...They become lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.69,0:22:52.45,Ed Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}itsudaatte
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.69,0:22:52.45,ED Hun,,0000,0000,0000,,As they do.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.03,0:22:54.70,Ed Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Girls in love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.03,0:22:54.70,ED Hun,,0000,0000,0000,,Girls in Love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.82,0:23:09.81,Ed Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}nee kono kimochi kimi igai wa arienai
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.82,0:23:09.81,ED Hun,,0000,0000,0000,,because when in love, this feeling says no one but you will do
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.05,0:23:11.67,Ed Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Girls in love
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.05,0:23:11.67,ED Hun,,0000,0000,0000,,Girls in Love
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.77,0:23:18.62,Ed Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Motto dakishimete yo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.77,0:23:18.62,ED Hun,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold me closer
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.63,0:23:28.36,Ed Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Yume no naka made tsuretette
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.63,0:23:28.36,ED Hun,,0000,0000,0000,,and take me to a world I can only dream about.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.99,0:23:33.43,Preview,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\pos(33,24)}Next Time:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.12,0:23:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomo-chan, and the training?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.20,0:23:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll boycott such meaningless training.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.70,0:23:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he's a singer's coach. Wouldn't it be bad to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.04,0:23:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care... I can't keep up that meaningless training.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.00,0:23:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kogure-san isn't here either, looks like it's going to turn into a big mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.05,0:23:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next Lemon Angel Project, episode 8: "Summer Angels in the Resort's Forest."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.80,0:23:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate the mustache demon!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.01,0:23:57.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mustache demon?? You're referring to director Katahige?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.74,0:23:59.70,PreviewTitle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fad(400,0)\pos(640,410)}Angels Of The Summer Resort's Forest